revised_prompt: Create an image that depicts a high-resolution, ethereal wrestling statistics dashboard background with a cosmic theme. This should include a dark purple-black gradient background with swirling golden nebulae. There should be floating holographic wrestling statistics written in glowing gold text indicating '87% WIN RATE', '342 PINS', '1,249 TAKEDOWNS', and 'POWER INDEX +5.1'. The image should also include translucent 3D bar charts and pie charts with gold accents showing performance metrics. Include subtle silhouettes of wrestlers in the background mist. Scattered golden particles and data streams should be shown flowing like constellations. Weight class numbers (106, 113, 120, 126, 132) should be floating as golden numerals. There should be ethereal glowing trophy icons. Overlay a hexagonal grid pattern at 10% opacity. Maintain a modern 4K resolution dashboard UI, mystical sports analytics visualization style with professional dark theme and luxury gold accents. Cinematic lighting should be used.
